    "causal_summary": "Phase 004 deletes the entire MCP tool surface for the four `deep_loop_graph_*` tools after phase 003 ships the `.cjs` script shims that consumers now invoke directly. The deletion removes five handler files under `mcp_server/handlers/coverage-graph/`, four entries in `tool-schemas.ts`, four entries in `schemas/tool-input-schemas.ts`, and four registration calls in the tools index. No aliases, wrappers, or transition layers remain; the MCP server still starts, and the four tool IDs are absent from `mcp tools list`.",
